title: Number of live births in the EU in 2018
yAxis: Number of live births in millions
summary: In general Number of live births in millions has stayed the same over the Year.
Number of live births in millions is roughly constant from 2014 to 2015, and lastly slightly decreasing from 2015 to 2018.
The steepest decrease occurs in between the Year 2017 and 2018.
Maximum Number of live births in millions, about 5.15 was reported at Year 2016
Minimum Number of live births in millions about 4.96 was reached at Year 2018
